Package sailpoint.object

Interface IntegrationExecutor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IntegrationInterface
    public interface IntegrationExecutor
extends IntegrationInterface
    Deprecated.
    The interface of a class that must be registered with an IntegrationConfig to process requests to an IDM system. You should no longer use this interface. Use sailpoint.integration.AbstractIntegrationExecutor instead.
